    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Element</strong>&nbsp;fire;&nbsp;<strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>substance infusion;&nbsp;<strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;6<strong>;&nbsp;Burn</strong>&nbsp;4<br><strong>Prerequisite</strong>&nbsp;flash infusion<br><strong>Associated Blasts</strong>&nbsp;blue flame, fire, plasma<br><strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none</p>\n<p>Your kinetic blast leaves an afterglow that banishes the darkness. Treat each square of the path of your ranged attack kinetic blast, the target square of your melee attack kinetic blast, or the area of your area of effect kinetic blast as the center of a&nbsp;continual flame&nbsp;effect that lasts until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>This effect counts as a 6th-level spell with the light descriptor.</p>",
